{"tid":2403272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大量灰色地帶 陳肇始答唔出","createTime":"2021-02-11T04:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T04:06:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d6155d88f7614bd70d9eaf6c1088211e5e0888ed","tid":2403272,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:02:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/AGT3X6MVLFGQRBNC3RMPYRJS6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2FAGT3X6MVLFGQRBNC3RMPYRJS6U%2F&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLC3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=b5aa5b02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2FAGT3X6MVLFGQRBNC3RMPYRJS6U%2F&h=68b90ab8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/AGT3X6MVLFGQRBNC3RMPYRJS6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n大量灰色地帶 陳肇始答唔出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PT7y5CJdVJjFSAmBszJ8RTn5tYk=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XQQEAVY4VZFL3NK3JPLKHMTDAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPT7y5CJdVJjFSAmBszJ8RTn5tYk%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXQQEAVY4VZFL3NK3JPLKHMTDAM.jpg&h=5c598512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳肇始昨用手接觸口罩表面，有違防疫常識。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】食衞局長陳肇始昨日形容疫情審慎樂觀，有條件放寬社交距離措施，但當局未有準則評定何謂疫情平穩。隨着政府趕推「安心出行」，當局亦未能釐清細節，例如如何確保顧客資料屬實、虛報資料責任誰屬等。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：堂食、處所鬆綁 顧客須用安心出行或留資料  初七硬上碼 違者停業判監<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吹噓抗疫有功 講到聲沙<br />\n<br />\n昨日疫情記者會近一小時，陳肇始開場發言佔了差不多三分一時間，其中最多篇幅是在自我吹噓政府抗疫「走在疫情前面」。在長氣發言到尾聲，她更一度聲沙及咳嗽。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始兩度被問到放寬社交距離措施的標準，是否每日確診宗數維持於單位數才可放寬，惟她未能提出確實數字，僅指如疫情沒有大爆發或大變化，有信心可於農曆新年後恢復社交生活。她其後補充，如疫情「持續𠵱家狀態，或者希望確診數字更加低」，當局會讓已關閉的處所重開。<br />\n<br />\n政府強制顧客使用安心碼，但存大量灰色地帶，多次被追問如何確保顧客留下真確資料、顧客若留下假資料時，應由誰人負責，。。。公告，「我哋有好多細節，喺發出嘅新聞公告，會講多啲細節畀大家聽」。<br />\n<br />\n另有記者質問本港疫情造成近200人死亡，政府會否向死者致歉，陳。。。。。治。"},{"pid":"0342781836334081ef068f96d6018ea8a2a369c4","tid":2403272,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:03:42.000Z","msg":"佢洗乜答得出<br />\n黑警先住執法同釋法果個"},{"pid":"9682af626125a8124ca4f096c76c9f17e10fe861","tid":2403272,"uid":125017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"都無諗過就做<br />\n點智答到"},{"pid":"289d388d5648fc8d6d790502cf52ca179a683132","tid":2403272,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:04:56.000Z","msg":"根本好難完全執行 但就搞黃店"},{"pid":"8703ee8f33f10b02d05e92a9565adeb2cc031539","tid":2403272,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:05:41.000Z","msg":"全世界打緊疫苗都敢講自己走在前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3fcd0f833aa35f90e8e1827c532b70a0d93056","tid":2403272,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SZH2Xp1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSZH2Xp1.png&h=15f2668e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XD2ivK1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXD2ivK1.jpg&h=01a4a18e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2SiBhp2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2SiBhp2.jpg&h=65e24a98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/coTmtwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcoTmtwH.jpg&h=b9a4f9ab&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}